            "title": "今日我咁睇｜聯儲局暫不考慮加息 息率壓力紓緩 恒指有望守穩 ｜小編苟豪",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/f1s7sz2oYGvHE50xBHqpQg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/9faa7f1f74c3a065264af6f86090dad7\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">1.美伊和談暫時未見成果，不過聯儲局就表明暫時可以容忍油價短期供應鏈問題帶來的通脹，不論原因是真的認為是短暫，還是向總統先口頭施加壓力，都表示聯儲局短期內不會加息，根據國債期貨數據，今年加息預期再次回到0。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2.美伊局勢估計最終還是走到邊打邊談的狀態，而跟隨特朗普講話去部署，不如像小編一樣跟油價去走，在100的位置開始造好股票，80的位置沽貨。當然，大家亦可以直接炒油價，看個人投資喜好。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3. 港股表現相對硬淨，現時在24500點上支持不錯，至於25000點相信阻力不太大，估計短期內可守穩，至於26000點就要看中東局勢發展。至少聯儲局短期不會緊急加息，算是好消息。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9f86b4f8-5e97-3bbe-940d-bfca60c60b15-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">4.選股方面，Minimax、智譜等AI大模型股，科網公司如阿里巴巴、美團等，都屬於可以吸納的股份，較進取者亦可考慮航空股，博油價又再回落。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">5. 恒指牛熊證街貨比例，熊證明顯高於牛證，相反理論反映短期大戶或向上挾殺熊證街貨，基本因素亦顯示向下的空間不大，值博率不錯。</p></div>",
